 夜晚<span style=\"color: red;\">十點咆哮</span>！（改9點會少好多人）<br />\n5. <span style=\"color: red;\">健身+運動</span>，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: red;\">每日一post</span>，國際戰線（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=e03e630b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n7. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n8. 保持<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考</span>，分析能力level up，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冷處理fake news/ rumour</span></strong> 、五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n<em>每星期任務：</em><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">低消費</span>，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">做孝子救港</span>，教育家中兩老<br />\n3. 去<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆</span>貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n<em>每月任務：</em><br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF轉美國<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會、陪審員、派傳單、放映會<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾；Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.16 @Template End@"},{"pid":"a2dc0fbed3d2100ae22a81469534caef81efff31","tid":1573450,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:40:43.000Z","msg":"白頭佬搏出鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6c54f9ba170dd9bf7b022aabb1e81be5567f33","tid":1573450,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2dc0fbed3d2100ae22a81469534caef81efff31","tid":1573450,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:40:43.000Z","msg":"白頭佬搏出鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:43:53.000Z","msg":"白頭佬GIF"},{"pid":"3af27d294a8cae3ad3d8a8b0db502061423efd2e","tid":1573450,"uid":306664,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DdvBDXC.png\" data